s-anhar"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-3Ij","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":754,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/05\/04\/five-prayers-remove-sins-like-water\/","url_meta":{"origin":14279,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Purification: Five prayers expiate sins like water removes dirt","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 4, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"If there was a river at your door\u00a0and he took a bath in it five times a day, would you notice any dirt on him?\" They said, \"Not a trace of dirt would be left.\" The\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14009,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/06\/waiting-prayer-fortress\/","url_meta":{"origin":14279,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Masjid: Waiting for consecutive prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cShall I not tell you of a deed by which Allah expiates your sins and raises your status?\u201d They said, \u201cOf course, O Messenger of Allah.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThorough ablution despite difficulty, taking many steps\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19124,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/12\/five-pillars-and-family-ties\/","url_meta":{"origin":14279,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Perform the five pillars, be kind to family","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 12, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ayyub reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cTell me what I can do to enter Paradise and avoid Hellfire.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cWorship Allah and do not associate anything with Him, perform the prayer, give in charity, and keep\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25400,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/09\/combine-salat-traveling\/","url_meta":{"origin":14279,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Travel: The Prophet combined prayers during travel","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 9, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, combined sunset and evening\u00a0prayers if he was undertaking a journey. And Ibn Abbas said, \u201cThe Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, combined the noon prayers and afternoon prayers\u00a0if he was on a journey, as well as\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17868,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/26\/only-practice-pillars-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":14279,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Only practicing the pillars of Islam?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 26, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: A man asked the Prophet, \u201cDo you think if I pray the five prescribed prayers, I fast the month of Ramadan, and I uphold what is lawful and unlawful without adding anything to it, will I enter Paradise?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYes.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33003,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/30\/perfect-wudu-five-salawat\/","url_meta":{"origin":14279,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Perfect ablution, five prayers expiation of sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 30, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Uthman ibn Affan reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever perfects his ablution as Allah Almighty has commanded him, the prescribed prayers will be an expiation for what occurs between them.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 231 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u062b\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14279","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp